		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Saint Paul</placeName> <date>October 20 5623</date>.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">Dear Sir&#33;</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">As I have to acknowledge<lb/> that you always did for me whatever you could&#44; and I<lb/> will never for get you&#44; I therefore take myself the<lb/> liberty&#44; to beg of you&#44; to give place to my writing to the<lb/> so called <persName>Doctor Wise</persName>&#44; who wish to injure me&#44; and who<lb/> is an enemy to any one whoever is not of his opinion&#59;<lb/> I am accused in his paper for having left a wife with<lb/> four children&#44; of which I did not wish to give him<lb/> any answer.  But to you indeed the truth of it is<lb/> when I left <placeName>New York</placeName> I was reengaged in <placeName>Nashville</placeName><lb/> directly after the engagement it was blockaded&#44;<lb/> at the same time I sent some money if I had any opportunity<lb/> after I came to <placeName>Memphis</placeName>&#44; directly&#44; when the blockade<lb/> was open I wrote to my wife.  But before I had an<lb/> answer from her I became sick and so I was obliged<lb/> to <sic>live</sic> <placeName>Memphis</placeName>&#44; and did not wish that another shall write<lb/> to my wife and after coming to <placeName>Davenport</placeName> I was in bed about<lb/> five weeks&#44; and that kept me beak<add>&#63;</add> from writing till being<lb/> a little better&#44; and when I came here on <add>Hebrew</add> you may ask<lb/> <persName>Mr Lion</persName> who was <add>Hebrew</add> in <placeName>Cleveland</placeName>&#44; and still it is only<lb/> he who keeps all the Israelites here to tune <add>&#63;</add> though being<lb/> himself a business man&#44; if I did not&#44; after speaking with<lb/> him one quarter of an hour&#44; write to my family&#44; where<lb/> I am and I hope to send for them as soon as possible<lb/> any how&#44; I will send them so much money as will be</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>in my power&#44; hoping that you will believe me<lb/> an <sic>especialy</sic> you may be convinced of the<lb/> truth thereof from <placeName>Memphis</placeName> from <placeName><sic>davenport</sic></placeName> and<lb/> from here I hope you will do so.</p>
				<p>Please God next week I will send you money<lb/> for a dozen of your Religious books.</p>
			<p rend="indent(10)">I remain</p>
			<p rend="indent(9)">Dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(10)">your most obedient</p>
			<p rend="indent(10)"><persName role="author">E. Marcuson</persName></p>
		</body>
